OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773338767
OL,3,CWe will not tolerate companies
OL,4,Cprofiteering from Middle East crisis `
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,8,Fvowed that the Government "will not
OL,9,Ftolerate" heating oil suppliers
OL,10,Fprofiteering from the crisis in the
OL,11,FMiddle East.
OL,13,FSir Keir will stress home heating oil
OL,14,Fcosts must be "fair, transparent and
OL,15,Fjustifiable", during a visit to
OL,16,FBelfast on Thursday.
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@IO]vD@OOUwD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
