PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773338767
OL,3,CWe will not tolerate companies
OL,4,Cprofiteering from Middle East crisis `
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FGlobal oil prices have risen sharply
OL,8,Fin response to war in the Middle East,
OL,9,Fwith Iran launching strikes in
OL,10,Fresponse to attacks by the US and
OL,11,FIsrael, and home heating oil costs
OL,12,Fhave surged.
OL,14,FThe market in Northern Ireland, unlike
OL,15,Fgas and electricity, is unregulated.
OL,17,FTreasury minister Lord Livermore met
OL,18,Fwith some Northern Ireland MPs on
OL,19,FWednesday to discuss the issue.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773338767
OL,3,CWe will not tolerate companies
OL,4,Cprofiteering from Middle East crisis `
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FThe Government said Sir Keir will use
OL,8,Fhis visit to Northern Ireland to
OL,9,F"highlight his relentless focus on
OL,10,Fcutting the cost of living for working
OL,11,Fpeople".
OL,13,FA statement said: "Recognising that
OL,14,Fthe majority of households in Northern
OL,15,FIreland rely on heating oil to heat
OL,16,Ftheir homes, the Prime Minister will
OL,17,Fsend the strong message to companies
OL,18,Fthat prices must be fair, transparent
OL,19,Fand justifiable, not inflated at the
OL,20,Fexpense of working people.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@GO]uD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773338767
OL,3,CWe will not tolerate companies
OL,4,Cprofiteering from Middle East crisis `
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,F"If companies hike prices without
OL,8,Fjustification, the Government will
OL,9,Fact, including through regulation."
OL,11,FThe Prime Minister said: "Global
OL,12,Finstability has real impacts on the
OL,13,Flives of working people across the UK,
OL,14,Fand I know families in Northern
OL,15,FIreland are worried about what the war
OL,16,Fin the Middle East could mean for
OL,17,Ftheir finances ` especially given so
OL,18,Fmany households rely on heating oil to
OL,19,Fheat their homes.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@cO]sD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773338767
OL,3,CWe will not tolerate companies
OL,4,Cprofiteering from Middle East crisis `
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,F"Let me be clear, we will not tolerate
OL,8,Fprofiteering or unfair practices.
OL,10,F"If companies fleece customers or rip
OL,11,Fthem off, we will not hesitate to step
OL,12,Fin, and that includes on regulation.
OL,14,F"This Government stands with working
OL,15,Fpeople, no matter the headwinds.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
