OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773338767
OL,3,CWe will not tolerate companies
OL,4,Cprofiteering from Middle East crisis `
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FIn a direct address today, Keir
OL,8,FStarmer confirmed that accelerating
OL,9,Fhousehold bill relief is now a top
OL,10,Fpriority, with a significant portion
OL,11,Fof the government's new strategy
OL,12,Finvolving a coordinated response to
OL,13,Fthe home heating oil market, which has
OL,14,Fseen prices surge due to ongoing
OL,15,Finternational tensions involving Iran.
OL,17,FThe Prime Minister has tasked the
OL,18,FTreasury Minister to talk with the
OL,19,FNorthern Ireland Executive about the
OL,20,Fheating oil-based heating in homes,
OL,21,Fand how a response can be co-ordinated.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
