PN,44409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1773338767
OL,3,CWe will not tolerate companies
OL,4,Cprofiteering from Middle East crisis `
OL,5,CStarmer
OL,7,FBeyond global market pressures, the
OL,8,Fgovernment expressed grave concerns
OL,9,Fregarding domestic price gouging.
OL,10,FOfficials warned that they are
OL,11,F"bearing down" on suppliers who are
OL,12,Funfairly inflating costs for consumers.
